♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

556
00:40:34,864 --> 00:40:39,224
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

557
00:40:39,224 --> 00:40:43,544
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

558
00:40:43,544 --> 00:40:47,984
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

559
00:40:47,984 --> 00:40:50,424
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

560
00:40:50,424 --> 00:40:54,504
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

561
00:40:54,504 --> 00:40:58,864
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

562
00:40:58,864 --> 00:41:03,224
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

563
00:41:03,224 --> 00:41:07,584
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

564
00:41:07,584 --> 00:41:11,944
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

565
00:41:11,944 --> 00:41:16,224
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

566
00:41:16,224 --> 00:41:20,784
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

